entry.title: [ANN] 0.10.0rc3 has been tagged
entry.summary: On January 12, 2015, Wladimir announced that the 0.10.0rc3 executables have been uploaded to https://bitcoin.org/bin/0.10.0/test. If users have already built rc2 from source, there is no need to build rc3. The announcement was signed with a PGP signature for security purposes.
